name: Kalendome_B3
description: Kalendome is a visual exploration of the Kaleidoscope aesthetic, started in 2015, the project uses timelapse photography from different places in Brazil.  Kelendome_B3 is based on a timelapse sequence from Rio de Janeiro city, RJ-Brazil. Shot at the Corcovado mountain.  MP4 video, 2048x2048px, 19 seconds, designed for flat and dome screens(dome master).
